  "Description": {
    "English": "Extreme pressure environments - such as deep water - cause elevated stress on the Exosuit's <span class=\"name name-technology\">oxygen circulation</span> and general life support systems.<br><br>Installation of this reinforced pressurisation shell increases <span class=\"name name-stellar\">efficiency</span> and <span class=\"name name-stellar\">protection</span> while operating in high-pressure environments.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "类似深海区域等极端压力环境会给套装的<span class=\"name name-technology\">氧气循环</span>以及常规维生系统带来巨大的压力。<br><br>安装这层强化增压外壳能够提高在高压环境下进行作业时的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">效率</span>与<span class=\"name name-stellar\">保护</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "極端壓力環境 (例如深水) 會導致強化套裝的<span class=\"name name-technology\">氧氣循環</span>和一般維生系統承受更大的壓力。<br><br>安裝這種強化增壓殼，能提升高壓作業環境下的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">效率</span>和<span class=\"name name-stellar\">防護</span>。"
  },
